Summary: noticed 3-4 lights in triangle formation during the delta 4 launch
divs: Sighting DetailsDuring the Delta 4 launch on the evening of August 7, 2013 I was able to capture 3-4 lights that formed a triangle formation that held formation while the Delta 4 released its boosters until the rocket went out of sight.
